      <ul>
        <li>New dwarf classes immediately</li>
        <li>Exclusive weapon skins</li>
        <li>Bonus starting minerals</li>
        <li>Special challenge modes</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950/20 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 my-8 rounded-r-lg">
